		<h2>About Us</h2>
		<p>The EAC Over 60s Art Awards competition is non-profit making and is run by EAC (<a href="http://www.eac.org.uk/">Elderly Accommodation Counsel</a>) a UK based housing advice charity.</p>
		<p>This unique combination, of an older people's free and independent advice charity and a nationally respected long-standing Seniors' Art competition, has its roots in a commitment to encourage and publicise the continuing talent and creative energy of those in later life.</p> 
