		<h4>Our Aims</h4>
		<ul class="disc thicker">
		<li class="li-spacing">To celebrate, showcase and reward the work of older artists - aged from 60 to 100+.</li>
		<li class="li-spacing">To foster and support opportunities for older artists to participate in creative activity, as not only rewarding in its own right, but also for its positive effect on overall physical and mental well-being.</li>
		<li class="li-spacing">To develop an online community of artists, and promote the use, benefits and joys of new technology, particularly among our older entrants.</li>
		</ul>
